    However, observers say the fiercely independent <a href="http://www.bg-group.com/" target="_new">BG</a> is expected to give the overture a cold shoulder and enter its own bid for the project, which includes a gas-fired 2,184 MW power plant and adjoining liquefied natural gas (LNG) jetty and storage... <a href="http://www.eyeforenergy.com/content.asp?nli=energy&nld=2/21/2002&news=25974"> 
